title: Should She Tell Her Neighbors What She Caught Their Daughter Doing Behind Their Back?
description:
Our listener recently witnessed her neighbor's teenage daughter having sex in the backyard when they were away. She feels awkward about the situation and isn't sure how to handle the situation. Should she tell the parents or not?
